graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    DSPO -->|platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.11+<br/>Required]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine| Argo[Argo Workflows v3.x<br/>Deployed by operator]
    DSPO -->|database| MariaDB[MariaDB 10.x<br/>Managed or External]
    DSPO -->|object storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Minio/ODF/AWS S3<br/>Required]
    DSPO -->|certificates| CertMgr[cert-manager or<br/>service-ca-operator<br/>TLS cert provisioning]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Pipeline management UI]
    DSPO -.->|legacy v1| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines Tekton<br/>DSP v1 backend deprecated]
    DSPO -->|distributed workloads| CodeFlare[Distributed Workloads<br/>CodeFlare<br/>AppWrapper CRD]
    DSPO -->|model serving| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService CRD]
    DSPO -->|distributed training| Ray[Ray<br/>RayCluster/RayJob CRD]

    %% Integration Points (reverse dependencies)
    Dashboard -->|calls KFP API| DSPO
    Pipeline[Data Science Pipelines] -->|deploy models| KServe
    Pipeline -->|submit jobs| Ray
    Pipeline -->|submit workloads| CodeFlare

    %% External Services (optional)
    DSPO -.->|alternative| ExternalDB[External MySQL/MariaDB<br/>Optional]
    DSPO -.->|alternative| ExternalS3[External S3 ODF or AWS<br/>Optional]

    %% Kubernetes Platform
    DSPO -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>Resource management<br/>Authentication]

    %% Monitoring
    DSPO -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics scraping]

